| 专访蔡霞（下）：特朗普的优势和习近平的“四大缺陷”</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"《自由亚洲 | 专访蔡霞（下）：特朗普的优势和习近平的“四大缺陷”》—中国数字时代\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/08/%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e4%ba%9a%e6%b4%b2-%e4%b8%93%e8%ae%bf%e8%94%a1%e9%9c%9e%ef%bc%88%e4%b8%8b%ef%bc%89%ef%bc%9a%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e7%9a%84%e4%bc%98%e5%8a%bf%e5%92%8c%e4%b9%a0%e8%bf%91/embed/#?secret=fw2Q1o1JBL\" data-secret=\"fw2Q1o1JBL\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n","author":1069,"categories":[18271,41492,38912,39487,38918],"tags":[13088,30129,10305,41509,23538,12308,40744,22766,41508,20865]}